title: Drawing, "Yellow Head, Left Profile"
description: The present head in left profile is tilted upward. The heavy black profile outline is shaded thickly in blue. The eye socket is blank under a curved eyebrow. The lips are closed and full.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Yellow Head, Left Profile".
13.5 x 8.5 cm (5 1/4 x 3 3/8 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-120.
